text: Larry Young may refer to: * Larry Young (musician) (1940–1978), jazz organist * Larry Young (umpire) (born 1954), baseball umpire * Larry Young (racewalker) (born 1943), Olympic racewalker * Larry Young, one of the many alter egos of the Marvel Comics anti-hero Deathlok * Larry Young, former President and CEO of Dr Pepper Snapple Group * Larry Young (politician) (born 1949), former Maryland State Senator * Larry J. Young, American psychiatrist
title: Larry Young
